# Performance Standards

## Image Optimization
- Use responsive images
- Implement lazy loading
- Optimize image formats
- Compress assets appropriately
- Use webp with fallbacks

## Component Loading
- Implement code splitting
- Use dynamic imports
- Lazy load off-screen content
- Optimize component chunks
- Minimize initial bundle

## State Management
- Avoid unnecessary reactivity
- Use computed properties efficiently
- Implement proper caching
- Optimize store actions
- Minimize state updates

## Rendering Optimization
- Use v-show for frequent toggles
- Implement virtual scrolling
- Optimize v-for directives
- Use keyed transitions
- Minimize DOM updates

## Resource Loading
- Implement route-level code splitting
- Prioritize critical resources
- Use preload for key assets
- Implement proper caching
- Optimize third-party scripts

## Build Optimization
- Enable tree shaking
- Minimize production builds
- Use modern build tools
- Implement proper chunking
- Optimize dependencies

## Monitoring
- Track core web vitals
- Monitor performance metrics
- Implement error tracking
- Use performance budgets
- Regular performance audits
